  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>The circuit cage and primary control sensors for a <span class=\"name name-technology\">primitive automaton</span>. Plans for a unit of this design were extracted from an <span class=\"name name-stellar\">autophage</span> left at an abandoned junker's camp, before being infused with an <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Atlas Seed</span>.<br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>为一台<span class=\"name name-technology\">基础自动装置</span>准备的电路笼与主控感应器。该设计单元的制作图提取自废弃拾荒者营地中的一个<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自噬体</span>，之后又融入了<span class=\"name name-fuel\">阿特拉斯之种</span>。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">原始機械生物</span>的電路框架及主要控制感應器。在被注入<span class=\"name name-fuel\">寰宇種子</span>之前，此設計單位的設計圖來自被棄置在廢棄拾荒者營地的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自噬</span>。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
